Agentic Spatial Data Engine for GeoZarr and DuckDB

Usage: eider [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  info         Discover dataset metadata
  extract      Extract Zarr data intersecting with vector polygons
  shell        Open an interactive DuckDB shell loaded with the data
  export       Export DuckDB query results to a Zarr array
  completions  Generate shell completion scripts
  search       Search a STAC API for GeoZarr assets
  resample     Temporally resample extracted GeoZarr data
  plot         Plot data from a local DuckDB file
  ingest       Convert legacy spatial files (NetCDF, GeoTIFF, CSV) to GeoZarr
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --output <OUTPUT>  Output format (table or json) [possible values: table, json]
  -h, --help             Print help
